msgid "authselect(8)"
msgstr "authselect(8)"

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "NAME"
msgstr "ຊື່"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:9
msgid "authselect - select system identity and authentication sources."
msgstr "authselect - ເລືອກແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຕົນ ແລະ ການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງລະບົບ."

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "ຮູບແບບການໃຊ້ງານ"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:13
#, no-wrap
msgid " authselect [--debug] [--trace] [--warn] command [command options]\n"
msgstr " authselect [--debug] [--trace] [--warn] ຄຳສັ່ງ [ຕົວເລືອກຄຳສັ່ງ]\n"

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:15
#, no-wrap
msgid "DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "ຄຳອະທິບາຍ"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:21
msgid ""
"*Authselect* is a tool to configure system identity and authentication "
"sources and providers by selecting a specific profile. Profile is a set of "
"files that describes how the resulting system configuration will look like. "
"When a profile is selected, *authselect* will create nsswitch.conf(5) and "
"PAM(8) stack to use identity and authentication sources defined by the "
"profile."
msgstr ""
"*Authselect* ແມ່ນເຄື່ອງມືໃນການຕັ້ງຄ່າແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຕົນ ແລະ ການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງລະບົບ ໂດຍການເລືອກໂປຣ"
"ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ສະເພາະເຈາະຈົງ. ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ແມ່ນຊຸດຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ອະທິບາຍວ່າການຕັ້ງຄ່າລະບົບ ຈະມີລັກສະນະແນວໃດ. ເມື່ອເລື"
"ອກໂປຣໄຟລ໌ແລ້ວ, *authselect* ຈະສ້າງ nsswitch.conf(5) ແລະ PAM(8) stack ເພື່ອໃຊ້ແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ"
"ຕົວຕົນ ແລະ ການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຕາມທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນໂປຣໄຟລ໌."

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:27
msgid ""
"If the provided profile set is not sufficient, the administrator may create "
"a custom profile by putting it in a special profile directory "
"({AUTHSELECT_CUSTOM_DIR}). By doing so, the profile is immediately usable by "
"*authselect*. See _authselect-profiles(5)_ for more information on extending "
"existing profiles."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າຫາກຊຸດໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີໃຫ້ຍັງບໍ່ພຽງພໍ, ຜູ້ດູແລລະບົບສາມາດສ້າງໂປຣໄຟລ໌ກຳນົດເອງໄດ້ໂດຍການເກັບໄວ້ໃນ ໄດເຣັກທໍ"
"ຣີໂປຣໄຟລ໌ພິເສດ ({AUTHSELECT_CUSTOM_DIR}). ເມື່ອເຮັດແນວນັ້ນ, ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ຈະສາມາດ ໃຊ້ງານໄດ້ທັນທີໂ"
"ດຍ *authselect*. ເບິ່ງ _authselect-profiles(5)_ ສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບການຂະຫຍາຍ ໂປຣ"
"ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີຢູ່."

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "OPT-IN TO AUTHSELECT"
msgstr "ການເລືອກໃຊ້ AUTHSELECT"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:39
msgid ""
"Authselect will not touch your existing configuration unless it has already "
"been created by it. If you want to start using authselect to configure your "
"system authentication, please call *authselect select* with *--force* "
"parameter first (e.g. *authselect select sssd --force*). The *--force* "
"parameter tells authselect that it is all right to overwrite existing non-"
"authselect configuration (see description below). Using the *--force* "
"parameter will automatically generate a backup of your current configuration "
"so if you wish to go back you can restore it with *authselect backup-"
"restore* command (see description below)."
msgstr ""
"Authselect ຈະບໍ່ແຕະຕ້ອງກັບການກຳນົດຄ່າທີ່ມີຢູ່ຂອງທ່ານ ນອກຈາກວ່າມັນໄດ້ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍຕົວມັນເອງ. ຖ້າທ່ານ"
"ຕ້ອງການເລີ່ມໃຊ້ authselect ເພື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງລະບົບ, ກະລຸນາໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ *authselect "
"select* ພ້ອມກັບພາຣາມິເຕີ *--force* ກ່ອນ (ຕົວຢ່າງ: *authselect select sssd --force*)"
". ພາຣາມິເຕີ *--force* ຈະບອກ authselect ວ່າອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ຂຽນທັບການກຳນົດຄ່າເດີມທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ມາຈາກ "
"authselect (ເບິ່ງຄຳອະທິບາຍດ້ານລຸ່ມ). ການໃຊ້ພາຣາມິເຕີ *--force* ຈະເຮັດການສຳຮອງຂໍ້ມູນ ການກຳນົ"
"ດຄ່າປັດຈຸບັນຂອງທ່ານໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ, ດັ່ງນັ້ນຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການກັບຄືນຄ່າເດີມ ທ່ານສາມາດ ກູ້ຄືນໄດ້ດ້ວຍຄຳສັ່ງ "
"*authselect backup-restore* (ເບິ່ງຄຳອະທິບາຍດ້ານລຸ່ມ)."

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:41
#, no-wrap
msgid "OPT-OUT FROM AUTHSELECT"
msgstr "ການຍົກເລີກການໃຊ້ AUTHSELECT"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:45
msgid ""
"To stop authselect from managing your configuration, run *authselect opt-"
"out*.  This will remove all authselect configuration from your system and "
"you can then modify your configuration manually."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອຢຸດໃຫ້ authselect ຈັດການການກຳນົດຄ່າຂອງທ່ານ, ໃຫ້ລັນຄຳສັ່ງ *authselect opt-out*. ນີ້ຈະເປັ"
"ນການລຶບການກຳນົດຄ່າທັງໝົດຂອງ authselect ອອກຈາກລະບົບຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນທ່ານສາມາດ ແກ້ໄຂການກ"
"ຳນົດຄ່າດ້ວຍຕົນເອງໄດ້."

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:47
#, no-wrap
msgid "AVAILABLE COMMANDS"
msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງທີ່ມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ງານ"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:50
msgid ""
"To list all available commands run *authselect* without any parameters.  To "
"print help for the selected command run *authselect COMMAND --help*."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອເບິ່ງລາຍຊື່ຄຳສັ່ງທັງໝົດທີ່ມີໃຫ້ ໃຫ້ລັນ *authselect* ໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງໃສ່ພາຣາມິເຕີໃດໆ. ເພື່ອເບິ່ງວິທີການໃຊ້ງາ"
"ນຂອງຄຳສັ່ງທີ່ເລືອກ ໃຫ້ລັນ *authselect ຄຳສັ່ງ --help*."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:51
#, no-wrap
msgid "*select* profile_id [features] [-f, --force] [-q, --quiet] [-b] [--backup=NAME]"
msgstr ""
"*select* profile_id [features] [-f, --force] [-q, --quiet] [-b] [--"
"backup=NAME]"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:54
msgid ""
"Activate desired profile. See profile description with *show* command, to "
"list profile specific optional features."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດໃຊ້ງານໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຕ້ອງການ. ເບິ່ງຄຳອະທິບາຍໂປຣໄຟລ໌ດ້ວຍຄຳສັ່ງ *show*, ເພື່ອເບິ່ງລາຍຊື່ ຄຸນສົມບັດເສີມສ"
"ະເພາະຂອງໂປຣໄຟລ໌ນັ້ນໆ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:55
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--force, -f*"
msgstr "*--force, -f*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:60
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Write changes even if the previous configuration was not created by\n"
"authselect but by other tool or by manual changes. This option will\n"
"automatically backup system files before writing any change unless\n"
"*--nobackup* option is set.\n"
msgstr ""
"ຂຽນການປ່ຽນແປງລົງໄປ ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າການກຳນົດຄ່າກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກສ້າງໂດຍ\n"
"authselect ແຕ່ມາຈາກເຄື່ອງມືອື່ນ ຫຼື ຈາກການປ່ຽນແປງດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ. ຕົວເລືອກນີ້ຈະ\n"
"ສຳຮອງໄຟລ໌ລະບົບໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດກ່ອນທີ່ຈະຂຽນການປ່ຽນແປງໃດໆ ນອກຈາກວ່າ\n"
"ຈະມີການຕັ້ງຕົວເລືອກ *--nobackup* ໄວ້.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:61 src/man/authselect.8.adoc:86
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:155 src/man/authselect.8.adoc:173
#, no-wrap
msgid "*-b*"
msgstr "*-b*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:66
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Backup system files before activating the selected profile. The backup\n"
"will be stored at {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. Current time with\n"
"unique string is used as a name of the backup. This is a shortcut\n"
"for *--backup=*.\n"
msgstr ""
"ສຳຮອງໄຟລ໌ລະບົບກ່ອນທີ່ຈະເປີດໃຊ້ງານໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກ. ຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງ\n"
"ຈະຖືກເກັບໄວ້ທີ່ {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. ເວລາປັດຈຸບັນພ້ອມກັບ\n"
"ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເປັນຊື່ຂອງການສຳຮອງ. ນີ້ແມ່ນທາງລັດ\n"
"ສຳລັບ *--backup=*.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:67 src/man/authselect.8.adoc:92
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:161 src/man/authselect.8.adoc:179
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--backup=NAME*"
msgstr "*--backup=NAME*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:71
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Backup system files before activating the selected profile. The backup\n"
"will be stored at {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. Current time with\n"
"unique string is used as a name if no value is provided.\n"
msgstr ""
"ສຳຮອງໄຟລ໌ລະບົບກ່ອນທີ່ຈະເປີດໃຊ້ງານໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກ. ຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງ\n"
"ຈະຖືກເກັບໄວ້ທີ່ {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. ເວລາປັດຈຸບັນພ້ອມກັບ\n"
"ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເປັນຊື່ ຖ້າຫາກບໍ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດຄ່າໃດໆ.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--nobackup*"
msgstr "*--nobackup*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "Do not backup system configuration even if *--force* is set.\n"
msgstr ""
"ບໍ່ຕ້ອງສຳຮອງຂໍ້ມູນການກຳນົດຄ່າລະບົບ ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າຈະຕັ້ງ *--force* ໄວ້ກໍຕາມ.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:75 src/man/authselect.8.adoc:166
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--quiet, -q*"
msgstr "*--quiet, -q*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:78 src/man/authselect.8.adoc:169
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The command will not print any informational message such as additional\n"
"profile requirements or backup location. Errors are still being print.\n"
msgstr ""
"ຄຳສັ່ງຈະບໍ່ສະແດງຂໍ້ຄວາມຂໍ້ມູນໃດໆ ເຊັ່ນ ຂໍ້ກຳນົດເພີ່ມເຕີມຂອງໂປຣໄຟລ໌\n"
"ຫຼື ສະຖານທີ່ເກັບຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງ. ແຕ່ຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຍັງຄົງຈະຖືກສະແດງຢູ່.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:79
#, no-wrap
msgid "*apply-changes* [-b] [--backup=NAME]"
msgstr "*apply-changes* [-b] [--backup=NAME]"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:85
msgid ""
"Re-apply currently selected profile. If the profile templates were updated "
"this command can be used to regenerate current system configuration in order "
"to apply these changes on the system. This command will only re-apply the "
"changes if the existing configuration is a valid authselect configuration, "
"otherwise an error is returned."
msgstr ""
"ນຳໃຊ້ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ໃນປັດຈຸບັນຄືນໃໝ່. ຖ້າມີການອັບເດດແມ່ແບບໂປຣໄຟລ໌ ຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ສາມາດ ໃຊ້ເພື່ອສ້າງການກຳ"
"ນົດຄ່າລະບົບປັດຈຸບັນໃໝ່ ເພື່ອນຳໃຊ້ການປ່ຽນແປງເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນລົງໃນລະບົບ. ຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ຈະນຳໃຊ້ການປ່ຽນແປງຄືນໃໝ່ກໍຕໍ່ເມື່ອກ"
"ານກຳນົດຄ່າທີ່ມີຢູ່ນັ້ນເປັນການກຳນົດຄ່າຂອງ authselect ທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງເທົ່ານັ້ນ, ບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນຈະສົ່ງຄ່າຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຄືນມາ."

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:91
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Backup system files before applying changes. The backup\n"
"will be stored at {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. Current time with\n"
"unique string is used as a name of the backup. This is a shortcut\n"
"for *--backup=*.\n"
msgstr ""
"ສຳຮອງໄຟລ໌ລະບົບກ່ອນທີ່ຈະນຳໃຊ້ການປ່ຽນແປງ. ຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງ\n"
"ຈະຖືກເກັບໄວ້ທີ່ {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. ເວລາປັດຈຸບັນພ້ອມກັບ\n"
"ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເປັນຊື່ຂອງການສຳຮອງ. ນີ້ແມ່ນທາງລັດ\n"
"ສຳລັບ *--backup=*.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:96
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Backup system files before applying changes. The backup will\n"
"be stored at {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. Current time with unique\n"
"string is used as a name if no value is provided.\n"
msgstr ""
"ສຳຮອງໄຟລ໌ລະບົບກ່ອນທີ່ຈະນຳໃຊ້ການປ່ຽນແປງ. ຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງຈະຖືກ\n"
"ເກັບໄວ້ທີ່ {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. ເວລາປັດຈຸບັນພ້ອມກັບຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນ\n"
"ຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເປັນຊື່ ຖ້າຫາກບໍ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດຄ່າໃດໆ.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:97
#, no-wrap
msgid "*list*"
msgstr "*list*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:99
msgid "List available profiles."
msgstr "ສະແດງລາຍຊື່ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ງານ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:100
#, no-wrap
msgid "*list-features* profile_id"
msgstr "*list-features* profile_id"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:104
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"List all features available in given profile.\n"
"_Note:_ This will only list the features without any description. Please, read the profile documentation with *show* to see what the features do."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງລາຍຊື່ຄຸນສົມບັດທັງໝົດທີ່ມີໃນໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ກຳນົດ.\n"
"_ໝາຍເຫດ:_ ນີ້ຈະສະແດງພຽງແຕ່ລາຍຊື່ຄຸນສົມບັດໂດຍບໍ່ມີຄຳອະທິບາຍ. ກະລຸນາອ່ານ ເອກະສານຂອງໂປຣໄຟລ໌ດ້ວຍຄ"
"ຳສັ່ງ *show* ເພື່ອເບິ່ງວ່າແຕ່ລະຄຸນສົມບັດໃຊ້ເຮັດຫຍັງ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:105
#, no-wrap
msgid "*show* profile_id"
msgstr "*show* profile_id"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:107
msgid "Print information about the profile."
msgstr "ສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບໂປຣໄຟລ໌."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:108
#, no-wrap
msgid "*requirements* profile_id [features]"
msgstr "*requirements* profile_id [features]"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:110
msgid "Print information about profile requirements."
msgstr "ສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບຂໍ້ກຳນົດຂອງໂປຣໄຟລ໌."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:111
#, no-wrap
msgid "*current* [-r, --raw]"
msgstr "*current* [-r, --raw]"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:115
msgid ""
"Print information about currently selected profiles. If *--raw* option is "
"specified, the command will print raw parameters as they were passed to "
"*select* command instead of formatted output."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກໃຊ້ໃນປັດຈຸບັນ. ຖ້າລະບຸຕົວເລືອກ *--raw*, ຄຳສັ່ງຈະສະແດງ ພາຣາມິເຕີດິບ"
"ຕາມທີ່ຖືກສົ່ງໃຫ້ຄຳສັ່ງ *select* ແທນການສະແດງຜົນໃນຮູບແບບປົກກະຕິ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:116
#, no-wrap
msgid "*check*"
msgstr "*check*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:120
msgid ""
"Check if the current configuration is valid (it was either created by "
"*authselect* or there are no leftovers from previous authselect "
"configuration)."
msgstr ""
"ກວດສອບວ່າການກຳນົດຄ່າປັດຈຸບັນຖືກຕ້ອງຫຼືບໍ່ (ບໍ່ວ່າຈະຖືກສ້າງໂດຍ *authselect* ຫຼື ບໍ່ມີສ່ວນເສດເຫຼືອຈາກການ"
"ກຳນົດຄ່າ authselect ກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້)."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:121
#, no-wrap
msgid "*test* profile_id [options] [features]"
msgstr "*test* profile_id [options] [features]"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:124
msgid ""
"Print content of files generated by *authselect* without actually writing "
"anything to system configuration."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງເນື້ອໃນຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ສ້າງໂດຍ *authselect* ໂດຍທີ່ຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ຂຽນຂໍ້ມູນໃດໆ ລົງໃນການກຳນົດຄ່າຂອງລະບົບແ"
"ທ້ໆ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:125
#, no-wrap
msgid "*-a, --all*"
msgstr "*-a, --all*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:127
#, no-wrap
msgid "Print content of all files.\n"
msgstr "ສະແດງເນື້ອໃນຂອງທຸກໄຟລ໌.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:128
#, no-wrap
msgid "*-n, --nsswitch*"
msgstr "*-n, --nsswitch*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:130
#, no-wrap
msgid "Print nsswitch.conf content.\n"
msgstr "ສະແດງເນື້ອໃນຂອງ nsswitch.conf.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:131
#, no-wrap
msgid "*-s, --system-auth*"
msgstr "*-s, --system-auth*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:133
#, no-wrap
msgid "Print system-auth content.\n"
msgstr "ສະແດງເນື້ອໃນຂອງ system-auth.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:134
#, no-wrap
msgid "*-p, --password-auth*"
msgstr "*-p, --password-auth*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:136
#, no-wrap
msgid "Print password-auth content.\n"
msgstr "ສະແດງເນື້ອໃນຂອງ password-auth.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:137
#, no-wrap
msgid "*-c, --smartcard-auth*"
msgstr "*-c, --smartcard-auth*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:139
#, no-wrap
msgid "Print smartcard-auth content.\n"
msgstr "ສະແດງເນື້ອໃນຂອງ smartcard-auth.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:140
#, no-wrap
msgid "*-f, --fingerprint-auth*"
msgstr "*-f, --fingerprint-auth*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:142
#, no-wrap
msgid "Print fingerprint-auth content.\n"
msgstr "ສະແດງເນື້ອໃນຂອງ fingerprint-auth.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:143
#, no-wrap
msgid "*-o, --postlogin*"
msgstr "*-o, --postlogin*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:145
#, no-wrap
msgid "Print postlogin content.\n"
msgstr "ສະແດງເນື້ອໃນຂອງ postlogin.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:146
#, no-wrap
msgid "*-d, --dconf-db*"
msgstr "*-d, --dconf-db*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:148
#, no-wrap
msgid "Print dconf database content.\n"
msgstr "ສະແດງເນື້ອໃນຂອງຖານຂໍ້ມູນ dconf.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:149
#, no-wrap
msgid "*-l, --dconf-lock*"
msgstr "*-l, --dconf-lock*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:151
#, no-wrap
msgid "Print dconf lock content.\n"
msgstr "ສະແດງເນື້ອໃນຂອງ dconf lock.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:152
#, no-wrap
msgid "*enable-feature* feature [-b] [--backup=NAME] [-q, --quiet]"
msgstr "*enable-feature* feature [-b] [--backup=NAME] [-q, --quiet]"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:154
msgid "Enable feature in the currently selected profile."
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ງານຄຸນສົມບັດໃນໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ໃນປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:160
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Backup system files before enabling feature. The backup\n"
"will be stored at {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. Current time with\n"
"unique string is used as a name of the backup. This is a shortcut\n"
"for *--backup=*.\n"
msgstr ""
"ສຳຮອງໄຟລ໌ລະບົບກ່ອນທີ່ຈະເປີດໃຊ້ງານຄຸນສົມບັດ. ຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງ\n"
"ຈະຖືກເກັບໄວ້ທີ່ {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. ເວລາປັດຈຸບັນພ້ອມກັບ\n"
"ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເປັນຊື່ຂອງການສຳຮອງ. ນີ້ແມ່ນທາງລັດ\n"
"ສຳລັບ *--backup=*.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:165
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Backup system files before enabling feature. The backup will\n"
"be stored at {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. Current time with unique\n"
"string is used as a name if no value is provided.\n"
msgstr ""
"ສຳຮອງໄຟລ໌ລະບົບກ່ອນທີ່ຈະເປີດໃຊ້ງານຄຸນສົມບັດ. ຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງຈະຖືກ\n"
"ເກັບໄວ້ທີ່ {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. ເວລາປັດຈຸບັນພ້ອມກັບຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນ\n"
"ຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເປັນຊື່ ຖ້າຫາກບໍ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດຄ່າໃດໆ.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:170
#, no-wrap
msgid "*disable-feature* feature [-b] [--backup=NAME]"
msgstr "*disable-feature* feature [-b] [--backup=NAME]"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:172
msgid "Disable feature in the currently selected profile."
msgstr "ປິດການໃຊ້ງານຄຸນສົມບັດໃນໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ໃນປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:178
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Backup system files before disabling feature. The backup\n"
"will be stored at {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. Current time with\n"
"unique string is used as a name of the backup. This is a shortcut\n"
"for *--backup=*.\n"
msgstr ""
"ສຳຮອງໄຟລ໌ລະບົບກ່ອນທີ່ຈະປິດການໃຊ້ງານຄຸນສົມບັດ. ຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງ\n"
"ຈະຖືກເກັບໄວ້ທີ່ {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. ເວລາປັດຈຸບັນພ້ອມກັບ\n"
"ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເປັນຊື່ຂອງການສຳຮອງ. ນີ້ແມ່ນທາງລັດ\n"
"ສຳລັບ *--backup=*.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:183
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Backup system files before disabling feature. The backup will\n"
"be stored at {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. Current time with unique\n"
"string is used as a name if no value is provided.\n"
msgstr ""
"ສຳຮອງໄຟລ໌ລະບົບກ່ອນທີ່ຈະປິດການໃຊ້ງານຄຸນສົມບັດ. ຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງຈະຖືກ\n"
"ເກັບໄວ້ທີ່ {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. ເວລາປັດຈຸບັນພ້ອມກັບຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນ\n"
"ຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເປັນຊື່ ຖ້າຫາກບໍ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດຄ່າໃດໆ.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:184
#, no-wrap
msgid "*is-feature-enabled* feature"
msgstr "*is-feature-enabled* feature"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:186
msgid "Check if feature is currently enabled in the selected profile."
msgstr "ກວດສອບວ່າຄຸນສົມບັດຖືກເປີດໃຊ້ງານຢູ່ໃນໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກຫຼືບໍ່."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:187
#, no-wrap
msgid "*create-profile* NAME [--vendor,-v] [options]"
msgstr "*create-profile* NAME [--vendor,-v] [options]"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:192
msgid ""
"Create a new custom profile named _NAME_. The profile can be based on an "
"existing profile in which case the new profile templates are either copied "
"from the base profile or symbolic links to these files are created if such "
"option is selected."
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງໂປຣໄຟລ໌ກຳນົດເອງໃໝ່ທີ່ມີຊື່ວ່າ _NAME_. ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ສາມາດອີງຕາມໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວ ເຊິ່ງໃນກໍລະນີນັ້ນ ແມ່ແບ"
"ບໂປຣໄຟລ໌ໃໝ່ຈະຖືກຄັດລອກມາຈາກໂປຣໄຟລ໌ຫຼັກ ຫຼື ສ້າງເປັນ symbolic links ໄປຫາໄຟລ໌ເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ ຖ້າມີການເລື"
"ອກຕົວເລືອກດັ່ງກ່າວ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:193
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--vendor,-v*"
msgstr "*--vendor,-v*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:196
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The new profile is a vendor profile instead of a custom profile. See\n"
"_authselect-profiles(5)_ for more information on profile types.\n"
msgstr ""
"ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ໃໝ່ແມ່ນໂປຣໄຟລ໌ຂອງຜູ້ຜະລິດ (vendor) ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນໂປຣໄຟລ໌ກຳນົດເອງ. ເບິ່ງ\n"
"_authselect-profiles(5)_ ສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບປະເພດຂອງໂປຣໄຟລ໌.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:197
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--base-on=BASE-ID, -b=BASE-ID*"
msgstr "*--base-on=BASE-ID, -b=BASE-ID*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:200
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The new profile will be based on a profile named _BASE-ID_. The base\n"
"profile location is determined with these steps:\n"
msgstr ""
"ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ໃໝ່ຈະອີງຕາມໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີຊື່ວ່າ _BASE-ID_. ສະຖານທີ່ຂອງໂປຣໄຟລ໌ຫຼັກ\n"
"ຈະຖືກກຳນົດດ້ວຍຂັ້ນຕອນເຫຼົ່ານີ້:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:201
#, no-wrap
msgid "If _BASE-ID_ starts with prefix _custom/_ it is a custom profile.\n"
msgstr "ຖ້າ _BASE-ID_ ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍຄຳນຳໜ້າ _custom/_ ມັນແມ່ນໂປຣໄຟລ໌ກຳນົດເອງ.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:202
#, no-wrap
msgid "Try if _BASE-ID_ is found in vendor profiles.\n"
msgstr "ລອງກວດສອບວ່າພົບ _BASE-ID_ ໃນໂປຣໄຟລ໌ຂອງຜູ້ຜະລິດ (vendor) ຫຼືບໍ່.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:203
#, no-wrap
msgid "Try if _BASE-ID_ is found in default profiles.\n"
msgstr "ລອງກວດສອບວ່າພົບ _BASE-ID_ ໃນໂປຣໄຟລ໌ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ (default) ຫຼືບໍ່.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:204
#, no-wrap
msgid "Return an error.\n"
msgstr "ສົ່ງຄ່າຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຄືນມາ.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:205
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--base-on-default*"
msgstr "*--base-on-default*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:208
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The base profile is a default profile even if it is found also within\n"
"vendor profiles.\n"
msgstr ""
"ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ຫຼັກແມ່ນໂປຣໄຟລ໌ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າມັນຈະຖືກພົບເຫັນໃນ\n"
"ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ຂອງຜູ້ຜະລິດ (vendor) ນຳກໍຕາມ.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:209
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--symlink-meta*"
msgstr "*--symlink-meta*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:212
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Meta files, such as _README_ and _REQUIREMENTS_ will be symbolic links\n"
"to the origin profile files instead of their copy.\n"
msgstr ""
"ໄຟລ໌ Meta ເຊັ່ນ _README_ ແລະ _REQUIREMENTS_ ຈະເປັນ symbolic links\n"
"ໄປຫາໄຟລ໌ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນສະບັບ ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນການຄັດລອກໄຟລ໌.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:213
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--symlink-nsswitch*"
msgstr "*--symlink-nsswitch*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:216
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"_nsswitch.conf_ template will be symbolic link to the origin profile\n"
"file instead of its copy.\n"
msgstr ""
"ແມ່ແບບ _nsswitch.conf_ ຈະເປັນ symbolic link ໄປຫາໄຟລ໌ໂປຣໄຟລ໌\n"
"ຕົ້ນສະບັບ ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນການຄັດລອກໄຟລ໌.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:217
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--symlink-pam*"
msgstr "*--symlink-pam*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:220
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"_PAM_ templates will be symbolic links to the origin profile files\n"
"instead of their copy.\n"
msgstr ""
"ແມ່ແບບ _PAM_ ຈະເປັນ symbolic links ໄປຫາໄຟລ໌ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນສະບັບ\n"
"ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນການຄັດລອກໄຟລ໌.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:221
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--symlink-dconf*"
msgstr "*--symlink-dconf*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:224
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"_dconf_ templates will be symbolic links to the origin profile files\n"
"instead of their copy.\n"
msgstr ""
"ແມ່ແບບ _dconf_ ຈະເປັນ symbolic links ໄປຫາໄຟລ໌ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນສະບັບ\n"
"ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນການຄັດລອກໄຟລ໌.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:225
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--symlink=FILE,-s=FILE*"
msgstr "*--symlink=FILE,-s=FILE*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:228
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Create a symbolic link for a template file _FILE_ instead of creating\n"
"its copy. This option can be passed multiple times.\n"
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງ symbolic link ສຳລັບໄຟລ໌ແມ່ແບບ _FILE_ ແທນທີ່ຈະສ້າງ\n"
"ໄຟລ໌ຄັດລອກ. ຕົວເລືອກນີ້ສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້ຫຼາຍຄັ້ງ.\n"

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:230
#, no-wrap
msgid "BACKUP COMMANDS"
msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງກ່ຽວກັບການສຳຮອງຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:232
msgid "These commands can be used to manage backed up configurations."
msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງເຫຼົ່ານີ້ສາມາດໃຊ້ເພື່ອຈັດການການກຳນົດຄ່າທີ່ສຳຮອງໄວ້."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:233
#, no-wrap
msgid "*backup-list* [-r, --raw]"
msgstr "*backup-list* [-r, --raw]"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:236
msgid ""
"Print available backups.  If *--raw* option is specified, the command will "
"print only backup names without any formatting and additional information."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງລາຍຊື່ການສຳຮອງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ມີໃຫ້. ຖ້າລະບຸຕົວເລືອກ *--raw*, ຄຳສັ່ງຈະສະແດງ ພຽງແຕ່ຊື່ຂອງການສຳຮອງຂໍ້"
"ມູນ ໂດຍບໍ່ມີການຈັດຮູບແບບ ຫຼື ຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:237
#, no-wrap
msgid "*backup-remove* BACKUP"
msgstr "*backup-remove* BACKUP"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:239
msgid "Permanently delete backup named _BACKUP_."
msgstr "ລຶບຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງທີ່ມີຊື່ວ່າ _BACKUP_ ແບບຖາວອນ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:240
#, no-wrap
msgid "*backup-restore* BACKUP"
msgstr "*backup-restore* BACKUP"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:243
msgid ""
"Restore configuration from backup named _BACKUP_. *Note:* this will "
"overwrite current configuration."
msgstr ""
"ກູ້ຄືນການກຳນົດຄ່າຈາກຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງທີ່ມີຊື່ວ່າ _BACKUP_. *ໝາຍເຫດ:* ນີ້ຈະ ຂຽນທັບການກຳນົດຄ່າໃນປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:245
#, no-wrap
msgid "OTHER COMMANDS"
msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງອື່ນໆ"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:247
#, no-wrap
msgid "*opt-out*"
msgstr "*opt-out*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:251
msgid ""
"Remove authselect configuration. This will restore nsswitch and PAM "
"configuration under its system location and authselect will no longer manage "
"it. Run *authselect select* to opt-in again."
msgstr ""
"ລຶບການກຳນົດຄ່າຂອງ authselect ອອກ. ນີ້ຈະກູ້ຄືນການກຳນົດຄ່າ nsswitch ແລະ PAM ກັບໄປຍັງສະຖານທີ່ຂ"
"ອງລະບົບ ແລະ authselect ຈະບໍ່ຈັດການມັນອີກຕໍ່ໄປ. ໃຫ້ລັນ *authselect select* ເພື່ອເລືອກໃຊ້ງານອີ"
"ກຄັ້ງ."

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:253
#, no-wrap
msgid "COMMON OPTIONS"
msgstr "ຕົວເລືອກທົ່ວໄປ"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:255
msgid "These options are available with all commands."
msgstr "ຕົວເລືອກເຫຼົ່ານີ້ສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້ກັບທຸກຄຳສັ່ງ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:256
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--debug*"
msgstr "*--debug*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:258
msgid "Print debugging information and error messages."
msgstr "ສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນການດີບັກ (debugging) ແລະ ຂໍ້ຄວາມຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:259
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--trace*"
msgstr "*--trace*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:261
msgid "Print information about what the tool is doing."
msgstr "ສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບສິ່ງທີ່ເຄື່ອງມືກຳລັງເຮັດຢູ່."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:262
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--warn*"
msgstr "*--warn*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:266
msgid ""
"Print information about unexpected situations that do not affect the program "
"execution but may indicate some undesired situations (e.g. unexpected file "
"in a profile directory)."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບສະຖານະການທີ່ບໍ່ຄາດຄິດ ເຊິ່ງບໍ່ມີຜົນຕໍ່ການເຮັດວຽກຂອງໂປຣແກຣມ ແຕ່ອາດບົ່ງບອກເຖິງສະຖານະ"
"ການທີ່ບໍ່ຕ້ອງການບາງຢ່າງ (ຕົວຢ່າງ: ພົບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ບໍ່ຄາດຄິດ ໃນໄດເຣັກທໍຣີໂປຣໄຟລ໌)."

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:268
#, no-wrap
msgid "TROUBLESHOOTING"
msgstr "ການແກ້ໄຂບັນຫາ"

#. type: Title ~
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:271
#, no-wrap
msgid "How can I tell if my system is using authselect?"
msgstr "ຂ້ອຍຈະຮູ້ໄດ້ແນວໃດວ່າລະບົບຂອງຂ້ອຍກຳລັງໃຊ້ authselect ຢູ່?"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:275
msgid ""
"Use *authselect check*. The output will tell you if you have 1) "
"configuration generated by authselect 2) non-authselect configuration or 3) "
"configuration that was generated by authselect but modified manually at some "
"point."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ *authselect check*. ຜົນລັນຈະບອກໃຫ້ທ່ານຮູ້ວ່າທ່ານມີ 1) ການກຳນົດຄ່າທີ່ສ້າງໂດຍ "
"authselect 2) ການກຳນົດຄ່າທີ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນຂອງ authselect ຫຼື 3) ການກຳນົດຄ່າທີ່ເຄີຍສ້າງໂດຍ "
"authselect ແຕ່ຖືກແກ້ໄຂດ້ວຍຕົນເອງໃນພາຍຫຼັງ."

#. type: Title ~
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:277
#, no-wrap
msgid "Is nsswitch.conf supposed to be a symbolic link now?"
msgstr "ຕອນນີ້ nsswitch.conf ຄວນຈະເປັນ symbolic link ແລ້ວແມ່ນບໍ່?"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:283
msgid ""
"Authselect generates your system configuration from scratch and stores it at "
"{AUTHSELECT_CONFIG_DIR}. System files are then created as symbolic links to "
"this directory. Symbolic links are used to make it clear that authselect is "
"now owning your configuration and should be used instead of any manual "
"modification."
msgstr ""
"Authselect ຈະສ້າງການກຳນົດຄ່າລະບົບຂອງທ່ານໃໝ່ທັງໝົດ ແລະ ເກັບໄວ້ທີ່ {AUTHSELECT_CONFIG_DIR}"
". ຈາກນັ້ນໄຟລ໌ລະບົບຈະຖືກສ້າງເປັນ symbolic links ໄປຫາ ໄດເຣັກທໍຣີນີ້. ການໃຊ້ symbolic links ແ"
"ມ່ນເພື່ອໃຫ້ຊັດເຈນວ່າຕອນນີ້ authselect ເປັນເຈົ້າຂອງການກຳນົດຄ່າຂອງທ່ານແລ້ວ ແລະ ຄວນໃຊ້ເຄື່ອງມືນີ້ແທນກ"
"ານແກ້ໄຂດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ."

#. type: Title ~
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:285
#, no-wrap
msgid "Error: Unexpected changes to the configuration were detected."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ: ກວດພົບການປ່ຽນແປງການກຳນົດຄ່າທີ່ບໍ່ຄາດຄິດ."

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:287
msgid "For example:"
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງ:"

#. type: delimited block .
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:293
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[error] [/etc/authselect/nsswitch.conf] does not exist!\n"
"[error] [/etc/nsswitch.conf] is not a symbolic link!\n"
"[error] [/etc/nsswitch.conf] was not created by authselect!\n"
"[error] Unexpected changes to the configuration were detected.\n"
"[error] Refusing to activate profile unless those changes are removed or overwrite is requested.\n"
msgstr ""
"[error] [/etc/authselect/nsswitch.conf] ບໍ່ມີຢູ່!\n"
"[error] [/etc/nsswitch.conf] ບໍ່ແມ່ນ symbolic link!\n"
"[error] [/etc/nsswitch.conf] ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກສ້າງໂດຍ authselect!\n"
"[error] ກວດພົບການປ່ຽນແປງການກຳນົດຄ່າທີ່ບໍ່ຄາດຄິດ.\n"
"[error] ປະຕິເສດການເປີດໃຊ້ງານໂປຣໄຟລ໌ ນອກຈາກວ່າການປ່ຽນແປງເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນຈະຖືກລຶບອອກ ຫຼື ມີການຮ້ອງຂໍໃຫ້ຂ"
"ຽນທັບ.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:297
msgid ""
"This means that your configuration is unknown to authselect and as such it "
"will not be modified. To fix this, please call *authselect select* with *--"
"force* parameter to say that it is all right to overwrite it."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າການກຳນົດຄ່າຂອງທ່ານບໍ່ເປັນທີ່ຮູ້ຈັກສຳລັບ authselect ແລະ ດ້ວຍເຫດນັ້ນ ມັນຈຶ່ງຈະບໍ່ຖືກແກ້ໄຂ. "
"ເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂບັນຫານີ້, ກະລຸນາໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ *authselect select* ພ້ອມກັບ ພາຣາມິເຕີ *--force* ເພື່ອຢືນຢັນ"
"ວ່າອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ຂຽນທັບມັນໄດ້."

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:299
#, no-wrap
msgid "RETURN CODES"
msgstr "ລະຫັດການສົ່ງຄ່າຄືນ"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:301
msgid "The *authselect* can return these exit codes:"
msgstr "*authselect* ສາມາດສົ່ງຄືນລະຫັດສະຖານະ (exit codes) ດັ່ງນີ້:"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:303
msgid "0: Success."
msgstr "0: ສຳເລັດ."

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:304
msgid "1: Generic error."
msgstr "1: ຂໍ້ຜິດພາດທົ່ວໄປ."

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:305
msgid ""
"2: Profile or configuration was not found or the system was not configured "
"with authselect."
msgstr ""
"2: ບໍ່ພົບໂປຣໄຟລ໌ ຫຼື ການກຳນົດຄ່າ ຫຼື ລະບົບບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າດ້ວຍ authselect."

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:306
msgid ""
"3: Current configuration is not valid, it was edited without authselect."
msgstr "3: ການກຳນົດຄ່າປັດຈຸບັນບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ, ມັນຖືກແກ້ໄຂໂດຍບໍ່ໄດ້ຜ່ານ authselect."

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:307
msgid ""
"4: System configuration must be overwritten to activate an authselect "
"profile, --force parameter is needed."
msgstr ""
"4: ຕ້ອງຂຽນທັບການກຳນົດຄ່າລະບົບເພື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ງານໂປຣໄຟລ໌ authselect, ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງໃຊ້ພາຣາມິເຕີ --"
"force."

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:308
msgid "5: Executed command must be run as root."
msgstr "5: ຄຳສັ່ງທີ່ໃຊ້ຕ້ອງລັນໃນຖານະ root (ຜູ້ດູແລລະບົບ)."

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:309
msgid "6: No configuration was detected."
msgstr "6: ກວດບໍ່ພົບການກຳນົດຄ່າໃດໆ."

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:311
#, no-wrap
msgid "GENERATED FILES"
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນ"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:314
msgid ""
"Authselect creates and maintains the following files to configure system "
"identity and authentication providers properly."
msgstr ""
"Authselect ສ້າງ ແລະ ດູແລໄຟລ໌ຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ເພື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າຕົວຕົນຂອງລະບົບ ແລະ ຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:315
#, no-wrap
msgid "*{AUTHSELECT_NSSWITCH_CONF}*"
msgstr "*{AUTHSELECT_NSSWITCH_CONF}*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:317
msgid "Name Service Switch configuration file."
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ກຳນົດຄ່າ Name Service Switch (nsswitch.conf)."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:318
#, no-wrap
msgid "*{AUTHSELECT_PAM_DIR}/system-auth*"
msgstr "*{AUTHSELECT_PAM_DIR}/system-auth*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:321
msgid ""
"PAM stack that is included from nearly all individual service configuration "
"files."
msgstr "PAM stack ທີ່ຖືກລວມເຂົ້າໃນເກືອບທຸກໄຟລ໌ກຳນົດຄ່າການບໍລິການແຕ່ລະອັນ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:322
#, no-wrap
msgid "*{AUTHSELECT_PAM_DIR}/password-auth, smartcard-auth, fingerprint-auth*"
msgstr "*{AUTHSELECT_PAM_DIR}/password-auth, smartcard-auth, fingerprint-auth*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:326
msgid ""
"These PAM stacks are for applications which handle authentication from "
"different types of devices via simultaneously running individual "
"conversations instead of one aggregate conversation."
msgstr ""
"PAM stacks ເຫຼົ່ານີ້ແມ່ນສຳລັບແອັບພລິເຄຊັນທີ່ຈັດການການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຈາກອຸປະກອນປະເພດຕ່າງໆ ຜ່ານການເຮັດວ"
"ຽກແຍກກັນພ້ອມກັນ ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນການເຮັດວຽກລວມກັນພຽງອັນດຽວ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:327
#, no-wrap
msgid "*{AUTHSELECT_PAM_DIR}/postlogin*"
msgstr "*{AUTHSELECT_PAM_DIR}/postlogin*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:335
msgid ""
"The purpose of this PAM stack is to provide a common place for all PAM "
"modules which should be called after the stack configured in system-auth or "
"the other common PAM configuration files. It is included from all individual "
"service configuration files that provide login service with shell or file "
"access. _NOTE: the modules in the postlogin configuration file are executed "
"regardless of the success or failure of the modules in the system-auth "
"configuration file._"
msgstr ""
"ຈຸດປະສົງຂອງ PAM stack ນີ້ແມ່ນເພື່ອເປັນບ່ອນກາງສຳລັບທຸກໆໂມດູນ PAM ທີ່ຄວນຈະຖືກເອີ້ນໃຊ້ ຫຼັງຈາກ "
"stack ທີ່ຕັ້ງຄ່າໃນ system-auth ຫຼື ໄຟລ໌ກຳນົດຄ່າ PAM ທົ່ວໄປອື່ນໆ. ມັນຖືກລວມຢູ່ໃນທຸກໄຟລ໌ກຳນົດຄ່າການບໍລິ"
"ການທີ່ໃຫ້ບໍລິການການເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບດ້ວຍ shell ຫຼື ການເຂົ້າເຖິງໄຟລ໌. _ໝາຍເຫດ: ໂມດູນໃນໄຟລ໌ກຳນົດຄ່າ "
"postlogin ຈະຖືກເຮັດວຽກ ໂດຍບໍ່ຄຳນຶງເຖິງຄວາມສຳເລັດ ຫຼື ຄວາມລົ້ມເຫຼວຂອງໂມດູນໃນໄຟລ໌ກຳນົດຄ່າ "
"system-auth._"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:336
#, no-wrap
msgid "*{AUTHSELECT_DCONF_DIR}/{AUTHSELECT_DCONF_FILE}*"
msgstr "*{AUTHSELECT_DCONF_DIR}/{AUTHSELECT_DCONF_FILE}*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:340
msgid ""
"Changes to dconf database. The main uses case of this file is to set changes "
"for gnome login screen in order to enable or disable smartcard and "
"fingerprint authentication."
msgstr ""
"ການປ່ຽນແປງໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ dconf. ຈຸດປະສົງຫຼັກຂອງໄຟລ໌ນີ້ແມ່ນເພື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າການປ່ຽນແປງສຳລັບໜ້າຈໍເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບຂອ"
"ງ gnome ເພື່ອເປີດ ຫຼື ປິດການໃຊ້ງານການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນດ້ວຍ smartcard ແລະ fingerprint."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:341
#, no-wrap
msgid "*{AUTHSELECT_DCONF_DIR}/locks/{AUTHSELECT_DCONF_FILE}*"
msgstr "*{AUTHSELECT_DCONF_DIR}/locks/{AUTHSELECT_DCONF_FILE}*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:343
msgid "This file define locks on values set in dconf database."
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ນີ້ກຳນົດການລັອກ (locks) ຄ່າຕ່າງໆທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ dconf."

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:345
#, no-wrap
msgid "SEE ALSO"
msgstr "ເບິ່ງເພີ່ມເຕີມ"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:346
msgid ""
"authselect-profiles(5), authselect-migration(7), nsswitch.conf(5), PAM(8)"
msgstr ""
"authselect-profiles(5), authselect-migration(7), nsswitch.conf(5), PAM(8)"
